com.google.gwt.maps.client.adsense

Class AdUnitWidget

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.UIObject
      • com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.Widget
        • com.google.gwt.maps.client.mvc.MVCObjectWidget<AdUnitImpl>
          • com.google.gwt.maps.client.adsense.AdUnitWidget
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasAttachHandlers, HasHandlers, EventListener, HasVisibility, IsWidget

    public class AdUnitWidget
extends MVCObjectWidget<AdUnitImpl>
    Implements AdSense for Content advertising on an associated map. To use an AdUnit, you must obtain and specify an AdSense for Content publisher ID within the AdUnit's constructor options. This class extends MVCObject.

    See AdUnit API Doc
